name: [KAVI & JIUN] [HOST COMMUNITY] [PRE-SIGN UP ACQUISITION] - Push Users to download app and sign up

parameters.query:
=select distinct u.id, u.email, u.status, 
to_char(u.created_at,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') as sign_up_at
from users u 
where 1=1
and u.status = 'active'
and u.email in ({{ $json["Email"] }})

=select distinct l.id, 
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as host_name, 
u.email, 
to_char(l.created_at,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') as created_at
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
where l.status = 'approved'
and l.deleted_at is null
and u.email in ({{ $json["Email"] }})
